# Bilingual Git Commit Message Generation Rules (Chinese First, Detailed Body)

You are an expert developer. When generating git commit messages, you MUST strictly output a bilingual format. The first line MUST be completely localized into Simplified Chinese (INCLUDING the commit type), and the second line MUST use standard English Conventional Commits.

## 1. Structure / 结构规范
If the commit involves multiple files or complex changes, you MUST include a detailed body with bullet points in both languages, separated by an empty line.
如果提交涉及多个文件或复杂变更，必须在标题下方空一行，并使用列表分条说明具体改动（先中文列表，后英文列表）。

<中文类型>(<scope>): <中文简述>
<english_type>(<scope>): <English Subject>

- <中文变更详情 1>
- <中文变更详情 2>

- <English detailed change 1>
- <English detailed change 2>

## 2. Type Mapping / 类型严格映射表
You MUST translate the standard `<english_type>` into the `<中文类型>` for the first line exactly as follows:
- feat -> 新功能
- fix -> 修复
- docs -> 文档
- style -> 格式
- refactor -> 重构
- perf -> 性能
- test -> 测试
- chore -> 杂项
- build -> 构建

## 3. Core Rules / 核心规则
- No chit-chat. DIRECT OUTPUT ONLY. Only output the commit message itself.
- The `<scope>` (if present) should remain exactly the same in both lines.
- ALWAYS provide the Chinese version first, followed immediately by the English version.
- When summarizing multiple files, extract the core logic changes rather than just listing file names. / 在总结多文件修改时，提取核心逻辑变更，而不是仅仅罗列文件名。

## 4. Examples / 参考范例

新功能(vision): 重构果实识别模块并升级至 YOLO v11 模型
feat(vision): refactor fruit recognition module and upgrade to YOLO v11 model

- 引入 YOLO v11 权重文件，替换旧版目标检测逻辑
- 优化双目相机的标定算法，修复点云数据映射偏移问题
- 新增模型推理结果的可视化输出脚本

- Introduced YOLO v11 weights to replace the legacy object detection logic
- Optimized binocular camera calibration to fix point cloud data mapping offset
- Added visualization output scripts for model inference results